# Walkthrough - Sakakibara Tax Website First View

I have completed the "First View" for the Sakakibara Tax Accountant Office website.
The design adheres to the specified color palette and "Japanese Corporate" aesthetic.

## Results

### Desktop View (1920px)
The desktop view features a full-screen hero image with vertical text (Tategaki) on the right, conveying a sense of tradition and trust.
![Desktop View](/C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/brain/b201d986-50f9-401f-8ee9-3535524926b0/desktop_view_1768348790304.png)

### Mobile View (375px)
The mobile view adapts the layout while maintaining the vertical text and background atmosphere. The navigation is hidden to focus on the key message.
![Mobile View](/C:/Users/hangy/.gemini/antigravity/brain/b201d986-50f9-401f-8ee9-3535524926b0/mobile_view_1768348814628.png)

## Verification
- **Colors**: Verified use of Deep Navy (#1F2A44), Gold (#BDAA4B), and Warm Gray (#F4F4F2).
- **Typography**: Verified Noto Serif JP for headings and Noto Sans JP for body.
- **Responsiveness**: Checked on 1920px and 375px widths. No overflow or layout issues found.
- **Code**: HTML5 and clean CSS architecture with BEM naming.

